我愿意接受这个概率
I'll take those odds.

171
00:11:21,090 --> 00:11:22,090
祝你好运 船长
Good luck, Captain.

172
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:24,050
我们都指望着你...
We're all counting on you...

173
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:25,510
飞行员
Airman.

174
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:36,690
XL -01呼叫任务控制中心 你收到吗？
XL-01 to Mission Control. Do you copy?

175
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:37,990
收到 XL -01
Copy, XL-01.

176
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:40,110
我准许你在四分钟内离开地球
I'm gonna grant you four minutes to be off planet,

177
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:42,110
但你要马上回来找我们
but then you come right back to us.

178
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,280
这是个命令
That's an order.

179
00:11:43,450 --> 00:11:44,450
收到
Roger that.

180
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:46,540
超速 我来了
Hyper Speed, here I come.

181
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:48,000
T减10...
T minus 10...

182
00:11:48,370 --> 00:11:49,370
...9...
...nine...

183
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:51,210
...8 7...
...eight, seven...

184
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,500
...六...
...six...

185
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:54,290
...五 四...
...five, four...

186
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,380
...三、二...
...three, two...

187
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,130
...一 启动
...one. Launch.

188
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,410
I. V. A. N.  请调出飞行计划
I.V.A.N., pull up the flight plan, please.

189
00:12:24,570 --> 00:12:25,620
你好 我是你的内部 --
Hello. I am your internal--

190
00:12:26,740 --> 00:12:27,870
自动导航仪
Autopilots.

191
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:35,080
你好 我是你的内部声控导航仪 请叫我I.V.A.N
Hello, I am your internal voice-activated navigator, call me I.V.A.N.

192
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:36,630
请准备好飞行计划 I.V.A.N
Ready the flight plan, please, I.V.A.N.

193
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:37,840
当然可以
Certainly.

194
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,090
你的任务是加速穿越深空
Your mission is to accelerate through deep space,

195
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:42,220
绕过阿尔法-特卡尼的弹弓
slingshot around Alpha T'Kani,

196
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:46,010
然后通过减速环回到塔卡尼主星这里
then through the deceleration rings back here to T'kani Prime.

197
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:49,430
目标飞行时间： 4分28秒
Target flight time: 4 minutes, 28 seconds.

198
00:12:49,850 --> 00:12:51,890
XL-01 你可以进行超级发射了
XL-01, you are clear for hyper-launch.

199
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:54,350
收到 控制 启动超速发射
Copy, control. Initiating hyper-launch.

200
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:20,960
接近50%的超速
Approaching 50 percent hyper speed.

201
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:27,300
燃料稳定
Fuel stable.

202
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:30,720
将速度提高到0.6c
Increasing speed to 0.6c.

203
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:35,850
百分之六十的超速
Sixty percent hyper-speed.

204
00:13:43,110 --> 00:13:46,490
增加速度至0.7c
Increasing speed to 0.7c.

205
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:52,790
百分之七十的超速
Seventy percent hyper-speed.

206
00:13:52,950 --> 00:13:54,040
燃料稳定
Fuel stable.

207
00:13:56,370 --> 00:13:58,750
接近0.8c
Approaching 0.8c.

208
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,460
推进到超速
Pushing to hyper-speed.

209
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:04,630
发动机1发生故障
Failure in Engine 1.

210
00:14:06,050 --> 00:14:07,800
燃料电池不稳定
Fuel cell unstable.

211
00:14:07,970 --> 00:14:08,760
I.V.A.N. 状态：
I.V.A.N., status.

212
00:14:08,930 --> 00:14:11,260
轨迹错误 加四度
Trajectory error, plus four degrees.

213
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:13,930
如果不纠正航向将导致错过星环
Failure to course-correct will result in missing the rings.

214
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:16,190
我们会飞向深空
We'll fly off into deep space

215
00:14:16,350 --> 00:14:17,600
导致必死无疑
resulting in certain death.

216
00:14:17,770 --> 00:14:19,020
是的 谢谢你
Yes, thank you.

217
00:14:19,190 --> 00:14:20,770
弹射是你唯一的选择
Ejection is your only option.

218
00:14:21,610 --> 00:14:22,730
不 不 我可以做到
No, no. I can do it.

219
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:27,110
警告： 你有26秒的时间来纠正航线
Warning. You have 26 seconds to course-correct.

220
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:30,410
你现在有25秒的时间来纠正航向
You now have 25 seconds to course-correct.

221
00:14:30,570 --> 00:14:32,160
-你现在有-- -请停止计数
-You now have-- -Stop counting, please.

222
00:14:32,330 --> 00:14:35,620
我很抱歉 我的安全协议禁止我终止倒计时
I'm sorry. My safety protocols prohibit me from terminating countdown.

223
00:14:35,790 --> 00:14:36,830
自动控制装置
Autopilots.

224
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,710
任务失败在即 请记录你的遗言
Mission failure imminent. Please record your last words.

225
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:42,750
今天不行 I.V.A.N.
Not today, I.V.A.N.

226
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:45,880
如果你对这个录音感到满意 请说话或选择1
If you are satisfied with this recording, speak or select 1.

227
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:48,720
I.V.A.N. 把引擎推到最大 最大功率
I.V.A.N., push the engines all the way. Maximum power.

228
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:51,850
这种行动是不可取的 燃料电池引爆 --
That action is inadvisable. Fuel cell detonation--

229
00:14:52,010 --> 00:14:53,970
这正是我所期待的
Is exactly what I'm counting on.

230
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:59,020
情况危急
Situation critical.

231
00:15:01,060 --> 00:15:02,900
燃料电池接近峰值容量
Fuel cell approaching peak capacity.

232
00:15:03,070 --> 00:15:04,440
打开燃料门 I. V. A. N.
Open up the Fuel Door, I.V.A.N.

233
00:15:04,610 --> 00:15:06,150
我很抱歉 我没有完全听清
I'm sorry. I didn't quite catch that.

234
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:08,610
-请重述你的命令 -打开燃料门！
-Please restate your command. -Open fuel door!

235
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:12,620
五分钟后引爆...
Detonation in five...

236
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:13,660
...四...
...four...

237
00:15:13,830 --> 00:15:14,990
...三...
...three...

238
00:15:15,160 --> 00:15:16,410
...二...
...two...

239
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:17,450
-... ...一 -现在！
-...one. -Now!

240
00:15:30,970 --> 00:15:32,430
航线已纠正
Course corrected.

241
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:34,220
你没能达到超速
You failed to reach hyper-speed.

242
00:15:34,850 --> 00:15:35,890
我不需要听到这个 I. V. A. N.
I didn't need to hear that, I.V.A.N.

243
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:37,020
你没听到？
You didn't hear that?

244
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:38,180
哦 我很抱歉 我再重复一遍
Oh, I'm sorry. I'll repeat.

245
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:40,640
-不 我听说--我是说-- -你没能达到超速
-No, I've heard-- I meant-- -You failed to reach hyper-speed.

246
00:15:40,810 --> 00:15:41,850
-谢谢你 I. V. A. N. -你没能达到--
-Thank you, I.V.A.N. -You failed to reach--

247
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:06,090
指挥官 你还好吗？
Commander, are you okay?

248
00:16:06,550 --> 00:16:09,260
迪亚兹 你长出了胡子
Diaz, you grew a beard.

249
00:16:09,420 --> 00:16:10,630
你是怎么长出胡子的？
How did you grow a beard?

250
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:11,840
哦 对了
Oh, right.

251
00:16:12,470 --> 00:16:13,640
首先 欢迎回来
First of, welcome back.

252
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:15,850
其次...
Secondly...

253
00:16:16,050 --> 00:16:16,970
等等
Wait.

254
00:16:17,350 --> 00:16:19,350
等等 这是什么？
Wait, what is this?

255
00:16:19,510 --> 00:16:20,970
我离开多长时间了？
How long was I gone?

256
00:16:21,190 --> 00:16:23,150
4年2个月零3天
Four years, two months and three days.

257
00:16:23,650 --> 00:16:24,730
什么？
What?

258
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:26,060
我以为我们已经失去了你 巴兹
I thought we've lost you, Buzz.

259
00:16:26,230 --> 00:16:28,400
艾莉莎 发生了什么事？
Alisha, what happened?

260
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:30,610
-时间膨胀 -什么？
-Time dilation. -What?

261
00:16:30,820 --> 00:16:32,650
时间膨胀很简单
Time dilation is quite simple.

262
00:16:32,860 --> 00:16:36,700
当你接近超速时 你的时间相对于我们的时间就变慢了
As you approached hyper-speed, your time slowed relative to our own.

263
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:39,200
所以 在你的任务中 你的年龄只有几分钟
So, during your mission you aged only minutes,

264
00:16:39,370 --> 00:16:41,250
而我们其他人却老了很多年
while the rest of us have aged years.

265
00:16:41,410 --> 00:16:43,040
简单地说：你飞得越快 --
Simply put: The faster you fly--

266
00:16:43,210 --> 00:16:46,590
我飞得越快 我就越能穿越到未来
The faster I fly the further into the future I travel.

267
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,880
我明白了
I get it.

268
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:53,510
那么 我们现在要做什么呢？
So, what are we gonna do now?

269
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:54,800
我不知道
I don't know.

270
00:16:54,970 --> 00:16:57,390
但我认为我们应该暂停更多的测试飞行
But I think we should hold off on any more test flights

271
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,430
直到我们想出别的办法
until we've figured out something else.

272
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,730
指挥官 我们说完成任务
Commander, we said finish the mission.

273
00:17:01,890 --> 00:17:03,100
这就是太空游侠的工作
That's what Space Rangers do.

274
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:04,690
以什么为代价 巴兹？
At what cost, Buzz?

275
00:17:04,850 --> 00:17:07,310
你愿意再损失四年时间吗？
Are you willing to lose another four years?

276
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:15,950
所以 大家只是被困在这里
So, everyone is just stuck here

277
00:17:16,570 --> 00:17:18,120
因为我
because of me.

278
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:30,300
嘿 你没事吧？
Hey, you all right?

279
00:17:31,130 --> 00:17:33,050
是的 是的 我很好
Yeah. Yeah. I'm fine.

280
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:35,430
等等 那是什么？
Wait, what's that?

281
00:17:36,010 --> 00:17:37,850
哦 我订婚了
Oh, I got engaged.

282
00:17:38,010 --> 00:17:40,850
哦 哇 那真是太好了 她叫什么名字？
Oh, wow. That's great. What's her name?

283
00:17:41,010 --> 00:17:43,640
Kiko 她是科学小组的成员之一
Kiko. She's one of the science crew.

284
00:17:44,390 --> 00:17:47,720
有趣的是 如果我们没有被搁浅 这根本就不重要
It's funny, it never would've mattered if we hadn't been stranded.

285
00:17:48,270 --> 00:17:50,110
你和你刚认识的人订婚了？
You got engaged to someone you just met?

286
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:53,030
巴斯 我三年前就认识她了
Buzz, I met her three years ago.

287
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,400
哦 对 对
Oh, right. Right.

288
00:17:56,410 --> 00:17:57,870
好吧 恭喜你 我很想见见她
Well, Congratulations. I'd love to meet her.

289
00:17:58,150 --> 00:18:00,870
嗯 有足够的时间 休息一下吧
Well, there's plenty of time for that. Get some rest.

290
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:03,290
这是个命令
That's an order.

291
00:18:09,380 --> 00:18:11,420
不客气！艾莉莎
YOU'RE WELCOME! ALISHA

292
00:18:26,770 --> 00:18:27,640
你好 巴兹！
Hello, Buzz!

293
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:31,480
我是索克斯 你的私人伴侣机器人
I am Sox. Your personal companion robot.

294
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:32,570
我的什么？
My what?

295
00:18:32,730 --> 00:18:33,940
我是星际指挥部派来的
I was issued by star command

296
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:37,110
来缓解你离开后的情绪变化
to ease your emotional transition after your time away.

297
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:40,950
哦 你考虑得真周到 机器猫
Oh, that's very considerate of you, robot feline.

298
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,330
不过不用了 谢谢你
But no thank you.

299
00:18:42,490 --> 00:18:44,240
恐怕这是规定
I'm afraid it's protocol.

300
00:18:44,870 --> 00:18:47,410
传感器显示你已经错过了四个生日
Sensors indicate you've missed four birthdays.

301
00:18:47,580 --> 00:18:49,500
你想要一个磨砂零食套装来庆祝吗？
Would you like a frosted snack kit to celebrate?

302
00:18:49,670 --> 00:18:52,290
不用了 那会影响到我的营养计划
Negative. That would compromise my nutritional regiment.

303
00:18:55,260 --> 00:18:57,970
我们可以谈一谈你的感受 我是一个优秀的倾听者
We can talk about your feelings. I am an excellent listener.

304
00:18:58,180 --> 00:19:02,260
不 不 听着 我有一个非常漫长的... ... 一天？
No, no. Look, I've had a very long... day?

305
00:19:02,430 --> 00:19:03,720
它没有按计划进行
It did not go as planned.

306
00:19:03,890 --> 00:19:05,770
任务不成功？
The mission was unsuccessful?

307
00:19:06,230 --> 00:19:07,350
肯定的
Affirmative.

308
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:10,980
哦 不 我很抱歉听到这个消息
Oh, no. I am so sorry to hear that.

309
00:19:11,650 --> 00:19:12,940
谢谢你 索克斯
Thank you, Sox.

310
00:19:13,150 --> 00:19:14,400
不客气 巴兹
You're welcome, Buzz.

311
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:15,980
我们玩个游戏好吗？
Shall we play a game?

312
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:17,400
-不 谢谢你 -你确定吗？
-No, thank you. -Are you sure?

313
00:19:17,570 --> 00:19:20,950
我可以根据你确切的性格特征 专门为你创造一个游戏
I can create a game specifically for you, based on your exact personality profile.

314
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:23,580
嘿 听着 索克斯 夥计 我很累了
Hey, listen, Sox, buddy, I'm pretty tired.

315
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:26,250
所以 我要先去打架了
So, I'm gonna go ahead and hit the rack.

316
00:19:26,410 --> 00:19:27,960
当然了
Of course.

317
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,960
如果你愿意 我可以提供睡眠声音
I can provide sleep sounds if you like.

318
00:19:33,170 --> 00:19:34,630
我有几个选择
I have several options.

319
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:37,260
夏天的夜晚 海洋的天堂 鲸鱼的叫声
Summer night, ocean ​​paradise, whale calls.

320
00:19:37,630 --> 00:19:39,260
不 不 白噪音就可以了
No, no. White noise is fine.

321
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:40,430
很好
Very well.

322
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:42,140
-晚安 索克斯 -晚安 巴兹
-Good night, Sox. -Good night, Buzz.

323
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:51,650
拉起来
Pull up.

324
00:19:52,020 --> 00:19:53,480
光年船长 你需要帮助吗？
Captain Lightyear, do you need help?

325
00:19:53,650 --> 00:19:54,650
不 我可以的
No. I can do it.

326
00:19:54,820 --> 00:19:55,820
巴斯 你确定吗？
Buzz, are you sure?

327
00:19:55,980 --> 00:19:57,320
恐怕这是规定
I'm afraid it's protocol.

328
00:19:57,570 --> 00:19:58,690
我可以的！
I can do it!

329
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:01,740
我可以做到的
I can do it.

330
00:20:01,910 --> 00:20:03,990
审查员表示你做了个噩梦
Censors indicate you had a nightmare.

331
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:06,620
-你想谈谈它吗？-不愿意
-Would you like to talk about it? -Negative.

332
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:09,370
好的 但记住 我的任务是帮助你
Okay, but remember, my mission is to help you.

333
00:20:09,580 --> 00:20:11,040
而且我不会放弃我的任务
And I'm not giving up on my mission.

334
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:12,370
是吗？
Yeah?

335
00:20:13,250 --> 00:20:14,250
是的
Yeah.

336
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:17,340
你知道吗 索克斯 我也不会放弃我的任务
You know what, Sox, I'm not giving up on my mission either.

337
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:19,670
太好了！那我能做什么？
Great! So what can I do?

338
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:23,260
好吧 你为什么不和你的老鼠夥伴交往
Well, why won't you engage with your mouse buddy.

339
00:20:24,970 --> 00:20:26,890
还有什么更有挑战性的吗？
Is there anything more challenging?

340
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:28,430
你想要挑战？好吧
You want a challenge? Okay.

341
00:20:28,970 --> 00:20:31,100
我想你可以研究一下这个燃料稳定性的问题
I guess you could work on this fuel stability thing.

342
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:34,610
晶体聚变 当然了
Crystalic fusion. Of course.

343
00:20:34,810 --> 00:20:36,110
我应该期待你什么时候回来？
When should I expect you back?

344
00:20:36,730 --> 00:20:38,110
大约4年
About four years.

345
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:41,820
等一下 你没必要这样做
Hold on. You don't have to do this.

346
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:43,610
指挥官 这是我的错误
Commander, this is my mistake.

347
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:45,070
我需要把它纠正过来
I need to make it right.

348
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:47,450
好吧 但也许我们应该考虑一下这个
Okay, but maybe we should think about this.

349
00:20:47,620 --> 00:20:50,290
考虑什么？来吧 我们是太空游侠
Think about what? Come on, we're Space Rangers.

350
00:20:50,450 --> 00:20:52,040
我们要完成任务
We finish the mission.

351
00:20:53,710 --> 00:20:55,580
好吧 这将是很好的再次穿上西装
Well, it would be nice to wear the suit again.

352
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:58,250
人们开始忘记太空游侠曾经的重要性
People are starting to forget Space Rangers ever mattered.

353
00:20:58,420 --> 00:21:00,670
好吧 我正要解决这个问题
Well, I'm about to fix that.

354
00:21:00,840 --> 00:21:02,130
到无限大
To infinity.

355
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,760
甚至更远
And beyond.

356
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,770
不稳定
UNSTABLE

357
00:22:17,580 --> 00:22:21,880
40周年快乐
HAPPY 40TH ANNIVERSARY

358
00:22:27,430 --> 00:22:27,930
不稳定
UNSTABLE

359
00:22:54,620 --> 00:22:55,700
嗨 巴兹
Hi, Buzz.

360
00:22:57,790 --> 00:23:00,000
你在一两年内回到这里...
You're back here in a year or two...

361
00:23:00,540 --> 00:23:03,960
而且 我不会
and, well, I won't.

362
00:23:04,710 --> 00:23:06,380
我不知道这是什么时候发生的
I don't know when it happened

363
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:10,510
但我似乎已经走了 变得很老了
but I seem to have gone and gotten very old.

364
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:15,180
我一直以为我们会再次成为太空游侠
I always thought we'd get to be Space Rangers again.

365
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:19,270
我怀念在星空中的日子
I miss being out among the stars.

366
00:23:19,730 --> 00:23:21,360
所有的冒险
All the adventures.

367
00:23:24,020 --> 00:23:26,030
但比起这些 我更想念
But more than any of that

368
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:28,240
我想念你
I missed you.

369
00:23:30,660 --> 00:23:31,780
嗨 奶奶
Hi, Grandma.

370
00:23:32,370 --> 00:23:34,580
嘿 亲爱的
Hey, sweetheart.

371
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:37,450
我给我的朋友巴斯留个口信
I'm leaving a message for my friend, Buzz.

372
00:23:37,620 --> 00:23:38,620
太空游侠？
The Space Ranger?

373
00:23:39,210 --> 00:23:40,710
是的
That's right.

374
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,630
他是在太空中现在
He's in space right now.

375
00:23:42,790 --> 00:23:43,790
哇
Wow.

376
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:46,090
这是我的孙女 Izzy
This is my granddaughter, Izzy.

377
00:23:46,260 --> 00:23:48,220
我也要成为一名太空游侠
I'm gonna be a Space Ranger too.

378
00:23:48,380 --> 00:23:49,380
就像他一样？
Just like him?

379
00:23:49,930 --> 00:23:50,930
就像你一样
Just like you.

380
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,680
再见 巴斯
Goodbye, Buzz.

381
00:23:57,220 --> 00:24:01,230
很抱歉我不能去看你完成任务了
I'm sorry I won't be there to see you finish the mission.

382
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,570
到无限大
To infinity.

383
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,440
还有更远
And beyond.

384
00:24:44,350 --> 00:24:47,230
敲门 敲门 对不起 打扰了 我刚刚搬进我的新...
Knock. Knock. Sorry to interrupt. I'm just moving into my new-

385
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:52,740
看那！真正的巴斯光年在肉体上
Look at that! The actual Buzz Lightyear in the flesh.

386
00:24:52,910 --> 00:24:53,910
肯定的
Affirmative.

387
00:24:54,130 --> 00:24:55,540
指挥官卡尔-伯恩赛德
Commander Cal Burnside.

388
00:24:55,660 --> 00:24:57,410
我小的时候是你的一个大粉丝
I was a big fan of your when I was a kid.

389
00:24:57,580 --> 00:25:01,580
好吧 那么我期待着与你合作 最终让我们离开这里
Well, then I look forward to working with you to finally get us out of here.

390
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:04,370
没有人告诉你吗？
Did no one tell you?

391
00:25:04,540 --> 00:25:05,750
告诉我什么？
Tell me what?

392
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:07,170
是的
Yeah.

393
00:25:08,870 --> 00:25:10,280
那是最后的任务 巴兹
That was the last mission, Buzz.

394
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:11,230
什么？
What?

395
00:25:11,320 --> 00:25:13,430
我们决定要继续留在这里
We've decided we gonna go ahead and stay right here.

396
00:25:13,590 --> 00:25:15,930
等等 这里？不行 这不是一个可行的选择
Wait, here? Negative, that is not a viable option.

397
00:25:16,090 --> 00:25:19,060
现在是了 看 我们正在建造这个
It is now. See, we're building this.

398
00:25:20,470 --> 00:25:22,100
激光防护罩
Laser shield.

399
00:25:22,850 --> 00:25:24,520
它可以把所有的人挡在外面
It'll keep all the creeters out.

400
00:25:24,690 --> 00:25:27,900
我们就躲在这里 用我们拥有的东西来做
And we'll just tuck right in here and make do with what we've got.

401
00:25:28,070 --> 00:25:30,860
凑合？不 等等 但你不明白 指挥官
Make do? No. Wait. But you don't understand, Commander.

402
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:33,490
我还是可以做到的 我可以让我们离开这里
I can still do it. I can get us outta here.

403
00:25:33,650 --> 00:25:35,570
老兄 你还相信这一点 真是太好了
Man, it's great you still believe that.

404
00:25:35,740 --> 00:25:36,990
但我们很好 巴兹
But we're good, Buzz.

405
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,950
得到了激光盾牌
Got the laser shield.

406
00:25:44,290 --> 00:25:45,750
哦 你好 巴兹
Oh. Hello, Buzz.

407
00:25:47,580 --> 00:25:48,590
巴斯？
Buzz?

408
00:25:53,050 --> 00:25:55,590
我有个好消息 巴兹
Well, I've got some good news, Buzz.

409
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:58,180
我想出了燃料的问题
I figured out the fuel problem.

410
00:25:58,510 --> 00:25:59,600
什么？
What?

411
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:01,560
这是一个有趣的组合
It was an interesting combination.

412
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:04,480
仅仅是最轻微的差异 但这就造成了所有的不同
Just the slightest variance, but that made all the difference.

413
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:07,270
索克斯 你是怎么做到的？
Sox, how did you do this?

414
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:11,530
我花了62年7个月又5天
It took me 62 years, seven months and five days.

415
00:26:11,690 --> 00:26:13,030
而且它很稳定？
And it's stable?

416
00:26:13,190 --> 00:26:14,240
理论上是的
Theoretically.

417
00:26:15,030 --> 00:26:17,820
我期待着在你的下一次任务中找到答案
I look forward to finding out on your next mission.

418
00:26:19,070 --> 00:26:20,280
是啊...
Yeah...

419
00:26:23,950 --> 00:26:24,960
什么？
What?

420
00:26:25,120 --> 00:26:27,540
晚上好 队长 我们是来接你的同伴机器人的
Evening, Captain. We're here to pick up your companion robot.

421
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:29,130
你是什么意思？
What do you mean?

422
00:26:29,290 --> 00:26:31,590
安全目的 你明白的
Security purposes. You understand.

423
00:26:31,750 --> 00:26:33,510
不 实际上 我不明白
No, actually, I don't.

424
00:26:33,670 --> 00:26:36,880
关闭程序 所以 我们必须让你的猫退役
Shutting down the program, So, we have to decommission your cat.

425
00:26:37,050 --> 00:26:38,260
这只需要一秒钟
It'll just take a second.

426
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:39,850
现在 等一下 只是...
Now, hold on, just...

427
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:45,060
至少让我来做
At least let me do it.

428
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,240
哇？
Whoa?

429
00:27:01,780 --> 00:27:03,160
巴斯 我们要去哪里？
Buzz. Where are we going?

430
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:04,330
我们要去太空
We're going to space.

431
00:27:04,490 --> 00:27:05,620
什么？
What?

432
00:27:06,910 --> 00:27:08,830
巴斯光年的任务记录 星际约会...
Buzz Lightyear mission log. Star date...

433
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:10,000
我不知道
I have no idea.

434
00:27:10,170 --> 00:27:12,250
在拥有稳定的燃料配方
In possession of stable fuel formula

435
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:15,130
我计划达到超速 这次终于完成了任务
I plan to reach hyper-speed and this time finally finish the mission.

436
00:27:15,300 --> 00:27:16,630
你在和谁说话？
Who are you talking to?

437
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:17,800
无所谓了
Doesn't matter.

438
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:21,470
巴斯 我的程序迫使我通知星际指挥部你已经走了...
Buzz, my programming compels me to notify Star Command that you have gone--

439
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,220
星际指挥部打算让你退役
Star Command was gonna decommission you.

440
00:27:23,390 --> 00:27:24,310
-什么？
-What? -That's right.

441
00:27:24,470 --> 00:27:26,180
熄灯 没有索克斯了
Lights out. No more Sox.

442
00:27:27,560 --> 00:27:29,140
嘿 你没有被授权进入这个区域
Hey! You're not authorized to be in this area--

443
00:27:31,730 --> 00:27:33,610
哇 我不知道你能这么做
Whoa, I didn't know you could do that.

444
00:27:33,770 --> 00:27:36,110
等一下 这是为我准备的 以防我越界？
Wait a minute, was that for me in case I got out of line?

445
00:27:36,280 --> 00:27:37,400
我给你争取了5分钟
I bought you five minutes.

446
00:27:52,710 --> 00:27:54,840
-好吧 索克斯 给我第一个 -罗杰
-All right, Sox, give me the first one. -Roger.

447
00:28:11,350 --> 00:28:12,900
好了 开始吧
Okay, here it goes.

448
00:28:16,440 --> 00:28:17,690
哇
Wow.

449
00:28:20,860 --> 00:28:22,200
这个公式！
The formula!

450
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:50,060
探戈到基地 探戈到基地 发射架上的安全漏洞
Tango to Base. Tango to Base. Security breach in the launch peg.

451
00:28:50,390 --> 00:28:51,390
爆炸
Blast.

452
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:54,020
我们有一个警卫倒下了 重复一遍 我们有一个警卫倒下了
We have a guard down. Repeat. We have a guard down.

453
00:28:56,980 --> 00:28:57,980
好的
Okay.

454
00:28:58,480 --> 00:28:59,320
你好
Hello.

455
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:02,200
-我是你的内部声控导航员 -不！I. V. A. N. ！不
-I'm your internal voice-activated navigator. -No! I.V.A.N.! No.

456
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:03,410
-你听到了吗？-叫我I.V.A.N
-Do you hear that? -Call me I.V.A.N.

457
00:29:03,570 --> 00:29:06,030
任务控制中心 在XL-15探测到活动
Mission Control, activity detected in XL-15.

458
00:29:06,530 --> 00:29:07,580
正在调查
Investigating.

459
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:08,740
收到
Roger that.

460
00:29:08,910 --> 00:29:10,620
XL-15 这里是控制中心
XL-15, this is the control.

461
00:29:10,790 --> 00:29:11,960
里面有人吗？
Is there someone in there?

462
00:29:12,120 --> 00:29:13,710
-说说看 -XL-15
-Say something. -XL-15.

463
00:29:13,870 --> 00:29:15,080
请回答
Please respond.

464
00:29:15,250 --> 00:29:19,090
收到 控制室 只是... ... 清洁人员
Copy, control. Just... the cleaning crew.

465
00:29:19,250 --> 00:29:22,510
我们正在清洁驾驶舱 清洁物品在这里？
We're cleaning the cockpit. Cleaning items in here?

466
00:29:22,970 --> 00:29:26,510
指挥官 我们是否批准了XL-15的驾驶舱清洗工作？
Commander, did we authorize the cockpit cleaning for the XL-15?

467
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,260
什么？没有
What? No.

468
00:29:31,890 --> 00:29:33,690
-停！回来！-等等！
-Stop! Come back! -Wait!

469
00:29:34,940 --> 00:29:38,190
XL-15 你违反了星际指挥部的规定
XL-15, you are in violation of Star Command protocol.

470
00:29:38,360 --> 00:29:39,570
立即停止你的行动
Cease your actions immediately.

471
00:29:42,150 --> 00:29:43,570
打开这个舱门！
Open this hatch!

472
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:46,450
指挥官 我是光年船长
Commander, it's Captain Lightyear.

473
00:29:46,620 --> 00:29:48,830
等等 什么？光年？把他救出来！
Wait? What? Lightyear? Get him out of there!

474
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,540
马上停下来 把你的手放在头上！
Stop right now and put your hands over your head!

475
00:29:57,210 --> 00:29:58,040
往后退
Back up.

476
00:29:58,210 --> 00:29:59,590
-我们需要后援 -让扎普巡逻队来
-We need back up. -Get the Zap patrol.

477
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,720
好了 队员们 我们走吧
All right, team. Let's go.

478
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:10,850
覆盖筒仓的门 他哪儿也不去
Override the silo doors. He isn't going anywhere.

479
00:30:13,310 --> 00:30:14,140
爆炸
Blast.

480
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:16,020
未经授权
Unauthorized.

481
00:30:20,770 --> 00:30:22,900
-未经授权 -来吧 我们在这里是坐以待毙
-Unauthorized. -Come on, we're sitting ducks here.

482
00:30:23,070 --> 00:30:24,070
请允许我
Allow me.

483
00:30:28,070 --> 00:30:30,370
-等等 发生了什么？-他推翻了我的超控
-Wait, what's happening? -He overrode my override.

484
00:30:30,530 --> 00:30:31,370
怎么会？
How?

485
00:30:44,210 --> 00:30:45,720
光年！
Lightyear!

486
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:46,930
我知道你能听到我
I know you can hear me.

487
00:30:47,090 --> 00:30:48,300
马上把飞船送回基地!
Return the ship to base right now!

488
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:49,300
否则就帮我...
Or so help me--

489
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:52,560
索克斯 让我们打破这个超速障碍 带大家回家
Sox, let's break this hyper-speed barrier and get everyone home.

490
00:31:04,610 --> 00:31:07,740
接近70%的超速
Approaching 70 percent hyper-speed.

491
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:15,790
接近80%的超速
Approaching 80 percent hyper-speed.

492
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,250
燃料稳定
Fuel stable.

493
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:21,460
90%的超速
Ninety percent hyper-speed.

494
00:31:27,930 --> 00:31:31,140
百分之百的超速
One hundred percent hyper-speed.

495
00:31:49,990 --> 00:31:51,700
恭喜你 光年船长
Congratulations, Captain Lightyear.

496
00:31:51,870 --> 00:31:53,780
你已经实现了超速
You have achieved hyper-speed.

497
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,870
我们成功了 索克斯 我们成功了！
We did it. Sox, we did it!

498
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,210
恭喜你 巴斯
Congratulations, Buzz.

499
00:32:00,370 --> 00:32:02,790
这真是太可怕了 我很后悔加入了你们
That was utterly terrifying, and I regret having joined you.

500
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,000
不 不
No, no.

501
00:32:06,170 --> 00:32:07,170
怎么了 巴兹？
What is it, Buzz?

502
00:32:07,340 --> 00:32:08,880
我们的速度仍然非常高
Our velocity is still extremely high.

503
00:32:09,050 --> 00:32:10,470
什么？哦 不！
What? Oh no!

504
00:32:10,630 --> 00:32:11,640
我们会坠毁吗？
Are we gonna crash?

505
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:12,800
不会
No.

506
00:32:12,970 --> 00:32:15,350
嗯 技术上是的 撑下去吧
Well, technically yes. Just hang on.

507
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:37,490
经过这么多年的努力 谢谢你 索克斯
After all these years. Thank you, Sox.

508
00:32:41,870 --> 00:32:43,080
任务记录 补充
Mission log, supplemental.

509
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:46,630
从星际指挥部借来一艘飞船后 我已经实现了超速
After borrowing a ship from Star Command I've achieved hyper-speed.

510
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:49,590
我已经准备好最终离开这个星球 一劳永逸
And I'm ready to finally leave this planet once and for all.

511
00:32:51,630 --> 00:32:53,890
巴斯光年呼叫星际指挥部 请回话 星际指挥部
Buzz Lightyear to Star Command. Come in, Star Command.

512
00:32:54,890 --> 00:32:56,100
星际指挥部 请回话
Star Command, come in.

513
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:58,100
他们为什么不回答？
Why don't they answer?

514
00:32:58,930 --> 00:32:59,930
嘿！
Hey!

515
00:33:00,100 --> 00:33:01,100
那些机器人
The robots.

516
00:33:01,560 --> 00:33:02,440
什么？
The what?

517
00:33:02,980 --> 00:33:04,770
机器人
The robots.

518
00:33:20,870 --> 00:33:22,000
等等 它在做什么？
Wait, what's it doing?

519
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,550
Zurg.
Zurg.

520
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:27,380
-我的飞船！-安静点
-My ship! -Be quiet.

521
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:28,550
它去哪了？
Where'd it go?

522
00:33:29,550 --> 00:33:30,550
在那上面
Up there.

523
00:34:11,070 --> 00:34:12,440
祖尔格
Zurg.

524
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:22,220
飞行员在哪里？
Where is the pilot?

525
00:34:23,810 --> 00:34:25,060
那是什么？发生什么事了？
What is that? What is going on?

526
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:26,520
蹲下
Get down.

527
00:34:29,690 --> 00:34:31,400
射击！来吧
Shoot! Come on.

528
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:36,570
他们一定也看到了你的船登陆
They must have seen your ship land too.

529
00:34:36,780 --> 00:34:38,320
-谁？-那些机器人
-Who? -The robots.

530
00:34:38,490 --> 00:34:41,200
为什么会有机器人？机器人是从哪里来的？
Why are there robots? Where did the robots come from?

531
00:34:41,370 --> 00:34:42,240
你从哪里来的？
Where did you come from?

532
00:34:42,410 --> 00:34:43,200
我是从这里来的
I came from here.

533
00:34:43,370 --> 00:34:44,750
在这里？等等
Here? Wait.

534
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:50,500
巴兹？
Buzz?

535
00:34:52,300 --> 00:34:53,170
阿利沙？
Alisha?

536
00:34:54,090 --> 00:34:56,260
哦 不 那是我的祖母 我是伊兹
Oh, no, that's my grandmother. I'm Izzy.

537
00:34:56,420 --> 00:34:57,430
伊兹？
Izzy?

538
00:34:58,510 --> 00:35:00,300
但你当时只是个小...
But you were just a little...

539
00:35:00,470 --> 00:35:01,560
索克斯 我们离开多久了？
Sox, how long were we gone?

540
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:02,720
喵喵
Meow meow.

541
00:35:02,890 --> 00:35:05,310
22年 19周又4天
Twenty-two years, 19 weeks and four days.

542
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:06,480
哇
Wow.

543
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:07,640
等等
Wait.

544
00:35:09,230 --> 00:35:10,360
来吧
Come on.

545
00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:13,530
在这里
In here.

546
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:19,240
我想我听到了一个
I thought I heard one.

547
00:35:19,450 --> 00:35:20,780
-一个机器人？-是的
-A robot? -Yeah.

548
00:35:21,330 --> 00:35:22,330
令人印象深刻
Impressive.

549
00:35:22,490 --> 00:35:24,290
嗯 我是霍桑人
Well, I am a Hawthorne.

550
00:35:24,450 --> 00:35:25,450
你当然是
You sure are.

551
00:35:25,620 --> 00:35:28,460
你知道吗 你奶奶和我几乎可以完成对方的句子
You know, your grandma and I could practically finish each other's sentences.

552
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:30,790
如果你像她一样 你和我就会成为--
If you're anything like her, you and I are gonna make--

553
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:32,460
-...一个伟大的团队 -...有些机器人会哭
-...a great team. -...some robots cry.

554
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:34,590
好吧...
Okay...

555
00:35:35,130 --> 00:35:37,590
所以 让我尽快了解这个
So, get me up to speed on this.

556
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:40,180
好的 Zurg飞船大约一周前出现了
Right. The Zurg ship showed up about a week ago.

557
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:41,350
什么是Zurg?
What's a Zurg?

558
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:45,310
机器人只说这个 所以我们就叫它大船
That's the only thing the robots say, so that's what we call the big ship.

559
00:35:45,470 --> 00:35:49,520
Zurg飞船到了 机器人包围了基地 然后... ...
The Zurg ship arrived, the robots surrounded the base, and then...

560
00:35:49,690 --> 00:35:53,070
T'kani主城的公民们 机器人外星人袭击了
Citizens of T'kani Prime, robot aliens have attacked.

561
00:35:53,230 --> 00:35:54,820
每个人都在周边的范围内
Everyone inside the perimeter.

562
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:55,860
小心！
Look out!

563
00:35:56,030 --> 00:35:58,110
我们立即启动激光防护罩
We are activating the laser shield immediately.

564
00:35:59,820 --> 00:36:01,620
这就是我们最后听到的消息
And that's the last we heard.

565
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:06,750
所有这些人 他们都指望着我
All these people, they were counting on me.

566
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,620
而现在他们被困住了
And now they're trapped.

567
00:36:09,870 --> 00:36:13,750
我们试图联系他们 但没有通信 不管是内部还是外部
We've tried to reach them, but there's no communication, in or out.

568
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,920
索克斯？
Sox?

569
00:36:15,090 --> 00:36:16,840
喵喵 她是正确的
Meow meow. She's correct.

570
00:36:17,620 --> 00:36:19,460
你把我和你的猫对上号了吗？
Did you check me against your cat?

571
00:36:19,630 --> 00:36:21,470
嗯 他不是你的标准猫科动物
Well, he's not your standard-issue feline.

572
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:23,640
事实上 索克斯是你奶奶送的礼物
Actually, Sox was a gift from your grandmother.

573
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:25,930
-你好 Izzy -你好 索克斯
-Hello, Izzy. -Hello, Sox.

574
00:36:27,220 --> 00:36:29,690
嘿 那是什么声音？来吧 别弄坏我的猫
Hey, what's that noise? Come on, don't break my cat.

575
00:36:29,850 --> 00:36:31,600
他在打呼噜 他喜欢这样
He's purring. He likes it.

576
00:36:31,770 --> 00:36:32,770
索克斯 你喜欢它吗？
Sox, do you like it?

577
00:36:32,940 --> 00:36:33,940
我喜欢
I do.

578
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:38,030
好吧 我希望你已经准备好行动了 因为我们需要的是一个飞行员
Well, I hope you're ready for action. Because all we needed was a pilot.

579
00:36:38,190 --> 00:36:39,190
为了什么？
For what?

580
00:36:39,360 --> 00:36:41,410
我有一个计划 我有一个团队
I have a plan and I have a team.

581
00:36:44,490 --> 00:36:45,660
来吧！
Come on!

582
00:37:11,730 --> 00:37:13,690
好了 队员们 集合了
All right, team, fall in.

583
00:37:17,230 --> 00:37:20,570
我找到了一个飞行员 惊喜派对行动已经开始了
I found a pilot. Operation Surprise Party is a go.

584
00:37:23,320 --> 00:37:26,660
我喜欢这个 一个精锐的小队 最好的中的最好的
I like this. An elite squad. The best of the best.

585
00:37:26,830 --> 00:37:30,580
你知道 她的祖母是军团历史上最伟大的太空游侠
You know, her grandmother was the greatest Space Ranger in the history of the Corps.

586
00:37:30,750 --> 00:37:32,040
能和你一起工作将是一种荣誉
It will be an honor to work with you.

587
00:37:32,210 --> 00:37:33,830
来吧 聚集在一起 团队
Come on, gather round, team.

588
00:37:36,750 --> 00:37:37,960
让我们回顾一下我们的目标
Let's review our objectives.

589
00:37:38,130 --> 00:37:39,130
杀死那些机器人
Kill the robots.

590
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:40,300
还有不要死
And don't die.

591
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:43,590
"不要死 "是你每天都想做的事情
"Don't die" is just something you wanna do every day.

592
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:44,760
这仍然是一个目标
It's still an objective.

593
00:37:44,930 --> 00:37:46,760
如果我可以的话 我们有一个目标
If I may, we have one objective.

594
00:37:46,930 --> 00:37:49,850
我们需要把这个水晶放进萝卜里 然后离开这里
We need to put this crystal in the turnip and get outta here.

595
00:37:50,270 --> 00:37:52,600
所以 要做到这一点 我们必须进入基地
So, to do that we have to get onto the base.

596
00:37:52,770 --> 00:37:55,100
要做到这一点 我们必须杀死所有的机器人
To do that we have to kill all the robots.

597
00:37:55,270 --> 00:37:57,610
要做到这一点 我们必须摧毁Zurg的飞船
To do that we have to destroy the Zurg ship.

598
00:37:57,770 --> 00:38:00,570
而要做到这些 我们就必须不死
And to do any of that we have to not die.

599
00:38:02,460 --> 00:38:03,320
德里克
DERIC

600
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:05,660
请允许我解释一下 "惊喜派对 "行动
Allow me to explain Operation Surprise Party.

601
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:08,580
它是 "雷霆之矛 "行动的一个变种
It is a variation on Operation Thunder Spear.

602
00:38:08,740 --> 00:38:09,990
你不是因为那次行动得到了一枚奖章吗？
Didn't you get a medal for that one?

603
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:11,790
实际上是两枚 但是...
Two, actually, but...

604
00:38:12,120 --> 00:38:14,160
等等 你怎么知道 "雷霆之矛 "行动？
Wait, how do you know about Operation Thunder Spear?

605
00:38:14,330 --> 00:38:16,920
我读过我奶奶所有的《太空游侠》书 从头到尾
I've read all my grandma's Space Ranger books, from cover to cover.

606
00:38:17,080 --> 00:38:18,130
两次
Twice.

607
00:38:19,830 --> 00:38:21,410
对不起 机器人猫咪
Excuse me, robot kitty.

608
00:38:21,590 --> 00:38:22,590
哦 对不起
Oh, sorry.

609
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:27,180
感应器显示Zurg飞船为地面上的机器人提供动力
Sensors have indicated that the Zurg ship powers the robots on the ground.

610
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:31,430
所以 我们飞到那里 炸毁那艘船 惊喜吧 机器人！
So, we fly up there, we blow up the ship. And surprise, robots!

611
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:32,720
你被烤焦了
You're toast.

612
00:38:32,890 --> 00:38:34,940
然后 我们把你的水晶放进萝卜里
Then, we put your crystal in the turnip.

613
00:38:35,100 --> 00:38:36,520
然后完成任务
And finish the mission.

614
00:38:37,270 --> 00:38:39,820
这是个好计划 为了无限大
It's a good plan. To infinity.

615
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:42,690
你想让我拉你的手指吗？
Are you trying to get me to pull your finger?

616
00:38:42,860 --> 00:38:43,860
别上当了
Don't fall for it.

617
00:38:44,030 --> 00:38:45,490
不 不是这样的 是...
No, not like that, it was...

618
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:48,370
对不起 这是你奶奶和我过去常做的事
Sorry, it's a thing your grandma and I used to do.

619
00:38:48,530 --> 00:38:49,530
恶心
Ew.

620
00:38:50,120 --> 00:38:51,790
我... ... 我们从来没有... ... 她不是故意...
I-- We were never-- She didn't mean to...

621
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:53,160
总之 忘了它 继续前进
Anyway, forget it. Moving on.

622
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:56,390
让我们把这些弹药装到犰狳号上
Let's load these munitions into the Armadillo

623
00:38:56,470 --> 00:38:57,790
并为战斗做好准备
and steel ourselves for combat.

624
00:38:57,880 --> 00:39:00,590
惊喜派对行动开始了
Operation Surprise Party is on.

625
00:39:01,710 --> 00:39:03,210
巴兹 你听到了吗？
Buzz, do you hear that?

626
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:04,630
我听到一些声音
I hear something.

627
00:39:07,470 --> 00:39:08,590
你认为是机器人吗？
You think it's a robot?

628
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:11,100
不 我们从来没有在离基地这么远的地方见过机器人
Nah, we've never seen a robot this far from the base.

629
00:39:11,260 --> 00:39:12,260
我什么都没听到
I don't hear anything.

630
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:14,140
现在我听到了
Now I do.

631
00:39:17,430 --> 00:39:18,570
Zurg.
Zurg.

632
00:39:22,770 --> 00:39:24,190
别担心 我们会照顾你的
Don't worry, we got you.

633
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:28,990
什么？
What?

634
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:30,450
训练用的弹药
TRAINING AMMO

635
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:33,540
不要害怕！少年巡逻队支持你
Fear not! The Junior Patrol has your back.

636
00:39:33,700 --> 00:39:34,700
少年什么？
The Junior what?

637
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:40,040
不 是飞船！
No! The ship!

638
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:47,590
我明白了吗？
Did I get it?

639
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:48,550
很接近
Pretty close.

640
00:39:48,720 --> 00:39:50,140
对不起 我没有受过这种武器的训练
Sorry, I'm not trained with this weapon.

641
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,090
让我重新装弹
Let me reload.

642
00:39:51,260 --> 00:39:53,430
没受过训练？等等 你说你 "没有受过训练 "是什么意思？
Not trained? Wait, what do you mean you're "not trained"?

643
00:40:05,730 --> 00:40:07,190
你在那里 抓住它！抓住它！
You there. Grab it! Grab it!

644
00:40:07,360 --> 00:40:09,700
抓住什么？
Grab what?

645
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:11,530
我不允许处理武器
I'm not allowed to handle weapons

646
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:13,530
这违反了我的假释规定
the violation of my parole.

647
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:14,490
假释？
Parole?

648
00:40:14,660 --> 00:40:15,240
巴兹！
Buzz!

649
00:40:15,410 --> 00:40:16,160
伊兹！现在！
Izzy! Now!

650
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,540
不！
No!

651
00:40:21,710 --> 00:40:22,960
好吧 新的计划
Okay, new plan.

652
00:40:23,170 --> 00:40:24,920
新计划？旧的计划是什么？
New plan? What was the old plan?

653
00:40:25,090 --> 00:40:26,670
我需要... 有人看到鱼叉了吗？
I need the-- Anyone seen the harpoons?

654
00:40:33,350 --> 00:40:35,180
他们预装了一个鱼叉 但我找不到... ...
They came preloaded with a harpoon, but I can't find--

655
00:40:35,350 --> 00:40:36,470
哦 我找到了
Oh, I found it.

656
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:39,350
我找到了鱼叉 我现在要重新装上它 看看这个吧
I found the harpoons. I'm gonna reload it now. Check this out.

657
00:40:49,190 --> 00:40:50,030
我找到了吗？
Did I get it?

658
00:40:50,200 --> 00:40:50,990
往左一点
A little to the left.

659
00:41:16,930 --> 00:41:17,930
什么？
What?

660
00:41:21,560 --> 00:41:22,390
我拍到了吗？
Did I get it?

661
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:23,650
你得到了它
You got it.

662
00:41:23,810 --> 00:41:24,860
是的！
Yes!

663
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,780
轰隆隆
Boom.

664
00:41:57,180 --> 00:42:00,560
好吧 好吧 到底是什么... ... 那是怎么...
Okay, okay. What exactly-- How did that--

665
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:01,730
你们是谁？
Who are you?

666
00:42:01,890 --> 00:42:04,060
我们是少年巡逻队 为你服务
We're the Junior Patrol, at your service.

667
00:42:04,230 --> 00:42:06,610
对了 我需要更多信息
Right, I'm gonna need more information.

668
00:42:06,770 --> 00:42:09,650
我们是一支由自我激励的学员组成的志愿者队伍
We are a volunteer team of self-motivated cadets.

669
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:12,690
我们每个月在前哨站这里训练一个星期
We train one week in a month here at the outpost.

670
00:42:12,850 --> 00:42:14,970
莫、达比和我是上周末机器人出现时第一个到达的人
Mo and Darby and I were the first to arrive last weekend

671
00:42:15,070 --> 00:42:16,320
当机器人出现的时候
when the robots showed up.

672
00:42:16,490 --> 00:42:19,280
因此 我们策划了 "惊喜派对行动"
So, we cooked up Operation Surprise Party.

673
00:42:19,450 --> 00:42:20,870
那么 你们是菜鸟？
So, you are rookies?

674
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:24,460
孩子 我们很想当菜鸟 还在为这个做准备
Boy, we'd love to be rookies, still building up to that.

675
00:42:24,790 --> 00:42:26,920
好的 你们有弹药训练吗？
Okay. Do you have munitions training?

676
00:42:27,080 --> 00:42:28,340
-部分 -战术训练？
-Partial. -Tactical engagement?

677
00:42:28,500 --> 00:42:29,710
-待定 -战斗经验？
-Pending. -Combat experience?

678
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:33,050
是的！如果你算上我们刚刚经历的机器人情况
Yes! If you count the robot situation we just went through.

679
00:42:33,220 --> 00:42:34,880
好的 来吧 索克斯
Okay. Come on, Sox.

680
00:42:35,050 --> 00:42:36,130
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

681
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:37,790
听着 你们看起来是好人
Look, you seem nice people.

682
00:42:37,870 --> 00:42:40,510
我非常支持你们的训练计划
I'm very supportive of your training initiatives.

683
00:42:40,600 --> 00:42:42,560
但我还是要继续下去 从这里开始
But I'm gonna go ahead and take it from here.

684
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:44,480
我们刚刚从那个机器人手里救了你
We just saved you from that robot.

685
00:42:44,640 --> 00:42:46,600
-请问？-小莫打了一枪
-Excuse me? -Mo made the kill shot.

686
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:48,060
Mo很幸运
Mo got lucky.

687
00:42:48,230 --> 00:42:49,230
非常
Very.

688
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:52,690
那么 如果你能给我指出另一艘飞船的方向
So, if you could just point me in the direction of another ship.

689
00:42:52,860 --> 00:42:56,240
在废弃的储存库里有可操作的航天器
There are operational spacecrafts at the abandoned storage depot.

690
00:42:56,410 --> 00:42:57,610
太好了 那是哪里？
Great. Where is that?

691
00:42:57,780 --> 00:43:01,200
储存库直接与资源重组中心相邻
The storage depot is directly adjacent to the Resource Reconstituting Center,

692
00:43:01,370 --> 00:43:04,750
距离你现在的位置有4.2公里
which is 4.2 kilometers from your current location.

693
00:43:04,910 --> 00:43:06,250
很好 那是什么地方？
Great. Where is that?

694
00:43:06,420 --> 00:43:07,790
这其实很简单
It's actually quite simple.

695
00:43:07,960 --> 00:43:09,290
好吧
Okay.

696
00:43:10,670 --> 00:43:12,880
你将首先向南朝基地走
You will first head south towards the base.

697
00:43:13,050 --> 00:43:15,010
经过两个红绿灯后 你会...
After two stop lights you will--

698
00:43:15,630 --> 00:43:18,510
等等 这是不对的 那是一个死胡同
Wait, that is not right. That is a dead end.

699
00:43:18,680 --> 00:43:21,010
哦 我明白了 我走错地方了
Oh, I see, I was in the wrong spot.

700
00:43:21,180 --> 00:43:23,390
对不起 我将重新开始
Apologies. I will start over.

701
00:43:23,560 --> 00:43:25,960
你将首先向南走向基地
You will first head south towards the base.

702
00:43:26,080 --> 00:43:30,110
过了两个红绿灯后 你会缓缓左转 然后... ...
After two stop lights you'll take a gentle left and--

703
00:43:30,190 --> 00:43:32,360
说吧 我又犯了一个错误
Shoot. I have made another error.

704
00:43:32,520 --> 00:43:33,530
我们就给你看看
We'll just show you.

705
00:43:33,690 --> 00:43:34,720
请允许我重新开始
Allow me to restart.

706
00:43:34,800 --> 00:43:37,150
你将首先向南走向基地
You will first head south towards the base.

707
00:43:37,240 --> 00:43:41,070
过了两个红绿灯后 你会向右转弯...
After two stop lights you'll take a hard right...

708
00:43:41,410 --> 00:43:43,160
巴斯光年补充任务日志
Buzz Lightyear supplemental mission log.

709
00:43:43,330 --> 00:43:44,890
在终于实现了超速之后
Having finally achieved hyper-speed

710
00:43:44,970 --> 00:43:47,540
现在我的道路上又多了一个障碍
I now have an additional obstacle in my way.

711
00:43:47,620 --> 00:43:52,590
为了逃离这个星球 我必须独自摧毁一艘巨大的外星飞船
In order to flee this planet I'll have to destroy a massive alien ship alone.

712
00:43:52,750 --> 00:43:54,380
而没有任何形式的援助
with no assistance of any kind.

713
00:43:54,550 --> 00:43:57,010
你知道 我们可以帮助你 这是我们的计划
You know, we can help you. It is our plan.

714
00:43:57,170 --> 00:43:58,180
我不能允许这样
I can't allow that.

715
00:43:58,340 --> 00:44:00,050
Star Command Code 2709.3
Star Command Code 2709.3

716
00:44:00,220 --> 00:44:03,350
3禁止我将不合格的人员置于危险境地
forbids me from placing unqualified personnel in harms way.

717
00:44:03,510 --> 00:44:05,310
好吧 但我是霍桑人
Okay, but I'm a Hawthorne.

718
00:44:05,470 --> 00:44:06,680
这不仅仅是一个名字 伊兹
It's more than just a name, Izzy.

719
00:44:06,850 --> 00:44:07,730
你必须清楚地知道 --
You have to know exactly--

720
00:44:07,890 --> 00:44:10,160
-在任何情况下如何反应... ...你接下来会说什么
-...how to react in any sit-- -...what you gonna say next.

721
00:44:10,240 --> 00:44:11,250
我想我有这个能力
I thought I had that one.

722
00:44:11,330 --> 00:44:12,110
好的
Okay.

723
00:44:12,270 --> 00:44:15,150
而你 你是在某种教养情况下？
And you, you're in a correctional situation of some kind?

724
00:44:15,320 --> 00:44:16,320
假释计划
Parole program.

725
00:44:16,490 --> 00:44:19,450
我做这个 他们给我减了点刑
I do this and they shave a little time off my sentence.

726
00:44:19,610 --> 00:44:21,410
但我在那里真的学到了很多东西
But I really learned a lot in there.

727
00:44:21,570 --> 00:44:23,580
达比可以把任何三样东西 让它们爆炸
Darby can take any three things and make them explode.

728
00:44:24,080 --> 00:44:25,950
好的 那你呢？ - 我？
Okay. And what about you?

729
00:44:26,120 --> 00:44:29,750
我以为这将是一个有趣的新兵训练营锻炼的事情
Me? I thought this was gonna be like a fun boot camp workout thing.

730
00:44:29,910 --> 00:44:31,240
但事实并非如此
But it is not.

731
00:44:31,410 --> 00:44:33,830
所以 我实际上是来这里交出我的东西的 --
So, I was actually coming out here to turn in my stuff--

732
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:35,090
他是个放弃者
He's a quitter.

733
00:44:35,300 --> 00:44:36,380
我不是放弃的人
I'm not a quitter.

734
00:44:36,550 --> 00:44:37,420
你是辞职了
You were quitting.

735
00:44:37,590 --> 00:44:39,800
你在说什么呢？我只是去了一个不同的方向
What are you talking about? I was just going in a different direction.

736
00:44:39,970 --> 00:44:41,510
是的 一个放弃者的方向
Yeah, the direction of a quitter.

737
00:44:41,680 --> 00:44:42,850
你知道吗 我放弃了
You know what, I give up.

738
00:44:43,010 --> 00:44:45,010
-你看 在你的右边...
-See? -On your right..

739
00:44:58,300 --> 00:44:59,190
祖格
Zurg.

740
00:44:59,280 --> 00:45:00,610
现在 我说到哪里了？
Now, where was I?

741
00:45:00,950 --> 00:45:02,410
我们到了 让我回去吧
Here we are. Let me back up.

742
00:45:04,200 --> 00:45:07,080
嘿 继续练习你的技能 这是让你变得更好的唯一方法
Hey, keep working on your skills. It's the only way to get better.

743
00:45:07,240 --> 00:45:08,250
我们可以帮助你
We can help you.

744
00:45:08,410 --> 00:45:10,910
我也很感激 只要回到你的训练设施中去
And I appreciate that. Just go back to your training facility.

745
00:45:11,080 --> 00:45:12,880
保持警惕 保持安全
Stay alert. Stay safe.

746
00:45:13,040 --> 00:45:15,060
我要去征用这架P-32犰狳战斗机
I'm going to commandeer this P-32 Armadillo

747
00:45:15,140 --> 00:45:16,630
然后去炸掉Zurg的船
and go blow up the Zurg ship.

748
00:45:16,710 --> 00:45:18,300
那么 这只是告别？
So, this is just goodbye?

749
00:45:18,590 --> 00:45:19,970
肯定的 再见
Affirmative. Goodbye.

750
00:45:22,340 --> 00:45:24,220
对不起 我忘了我的猫
Sorry, I forgot my cat.

751
00:45:34,810 --> 00:45:36,150
检测到生命体
Life forms detected.

752
00:45:36,400 --> 00:45:37,360
它们是什么？
What are they?

753
00:45:37,520 --> 00:45:39,140
巨大的昆虫类生物
Giant insectoid organisms.

754
00:45:39,780 --> 00:45:41,820
这座建筑似乎是某种蜂巢
The building appears to be some sort of hive.

755
00:45:41,990 --> 00:45:42,910
它们有威胁吗？
Are they a threat?

756
00:45:43,070 --> 00:45:44,740
传感器显示它们正在冬眠
Sensors indicate they are hibernating.

757
00:45:44,910 --> 00:45:45,910
非常好
Very good.

758
00:45:46,490 --> 00:45:47,740
哦 看！
Oh, look!

759
00:45:47,910 --> 00:45:49,450
那是XL -01
It's the XL-01.

760
00:45:49,750 --> 00:45:51,290
已经很久没有...
It's been a long time since...

761
00:45:51,790 --> 00:45:52,710
哇哦
Whoa.

762
00:45:52,790 --> 00:45:53,790
这是什么？
What is it?

763
00:45:53,960 --> 00:45:55,380
来吧 我给你看
Come on, I'll show you.

764
00:46:10,560 --> 00:46:11,850
终于来了
Finally.

765
00:46:15,650 --> 00:46:16,650
对不起 打断一下
Sorry to interrupt.

766
00:46:16,810 --> 00:46:18,360
看起来你正在享受一个真正美好的时刻
Looks like you were having a real nice moment.

767
00:46:18,520 --> 00:46:19,900
你在这里做什么？这不安全
What are you doing here? It's not safe.

768
00:46:20,110 --> 00:46:21,400
你拿了我们卡车的钥匙
You took the keys to our truck.

769
00:46:21,570 --> 00:46:22,570
他们在那里
There they are.

770
00:46:27,910 --> 00:46:29,160
来吧 来吧 来吧
Come on. Come on.

771
00:46:29,330 --> 00:46:30,410
-安静 -我正在努力
-Quiet. -I'm trying.

772
00:46:32,200 --> 00:46:33,500
明白了
Got it.

773
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:38,000
-谁去... ... -去开门！
-Somebody get-- -Get the door!

774
00:46:40,380 --> 00:46:41,710
你想说 "开门" 而我已经开门了
You were gonna say "get the door", and I got the door.

775
00:46:44,050 --> 00:46:46,510
好吧 我就直说了吧 我希望这事没有发生
Well, I'm gonna be blunt here. I wish that hadn't happened.

776
00:46:46,680 --> 00:46:47,970
我们其他人也是如此
So did the rest of us.

777
00:46:48,140 --> 00:46:49,140
每个人都拿起武器
Everyone grab a weapon.

778
00:46:49,300 --> 00:46:51,350
孩子 我也想 但我的假释... ...
Boy, I'd love to, but my parole--

779
00:46:51,520 --> 00:46:53,850
作为一名星际指挥官 我授予你紧急权力
As a Star Command Officer I grant you emergency authority.

780
00:46:54,020 --> 00:46:55,520
我们要用爆炸的方式离开这里
We're gonna blast our way outta here.

781
00:46:55,690 --> 00:46:56,600
现在我们正在谈论！
Now we're talking!

782
00:46:56,770 --> 00:47:00,400
巴斯 正面攻击的生存概率是38. 2%
Buzz, the probability of survival a frontal attack is 38.2 percent.

783
00:47:00,570 --> 00:47:01,730
似乎有点低
Seems a bit low.

784
00:47:01,900 --> 00:47:03,030
那隐身模式呢？
What about Stealth Mode?

785
00:47:03,190 --> 00:47:04,360
你怎么知道隐身模式的？
How do you know about Stealth Mode?

786
00:47:04,530 --> 00:47:06,530
祖母和我过去一直在玩隐身模式
Grandma and I used to play Stealth Mode all the time.

787
00:47:06,700 --> 00:47:08,300
这就像捉迷藏 但有一个转折
It was like hide-and-seek, but with a twist.

788
00:47:08,490 --> 00:47:11,990
好吧 其实这是很好的想法 我将使用隐身模式来迷惑他们
Okay, well, it's actually good thinking. I'll use Stealth Mode to disorient them.

789
00:47:12,160 --> 00:47:14,080
或者 在这里坚持我的观点
Or, and stick with me here.

790
00:47:14,230 --> 00:47:17,280
我们都可以使用隐身模式 直接走出去
We could all use Stealth Mode and just walk right out.

791
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:20,880
你是说 你会穿上太空游侠的衣服？
You mean, you would wear a Space Ranger suit?

792
00:47:21,040 --> 00:47:22,880
这套衣服上已经有我的名字了
This one already has my name on it.

793
00:47:25,470 --> 00:47:26,720
好的
Okay.

794
00:47:27,510 --> 00:47:28,510
让我们回顾一下
Let's review.

795
00:47:28,680 --> 00:47:29,550
我去...
I'm going--

796
00:47:29,720 --> 00:47:30,720
那边走
That way.

797
00:47:30,890 --> 00:47:31,760
而你要去...
And you're going--

798
00:47:31,930 --> 00:47:33,020
那边
That way.

799
00:47:33,180 --> 00:47:34,180
好的 非常好
Okay. Very good.

800
00:47:34,350 --> 00:47:36,980
看看吧 我是羽毛... 羽毛... ...
Check it out, I'm Feathers... Feathering...

801
00:47:38,100 --> 00:47:39,810
哦 看 一支笔 真酷
Oh, look, a pen. Cool.

802
00:47:39,980 --> 00:47:42,020
-你的有笔吗？-好了 注意了
-Does yours have a pen? -Okay, pay attention.

803
00:47:42,190 --> 00:47:43,400
隐身模式是相当简单的
Stealth mode is fairly simple.

804
00:47:43,730 --> 00:47:45,650
只有两个部分 你按下这个按钮--
There are just two parts. You press the button--

805
00:47:45,820 --> 00:47:47,990
-是这个按钮吗？-我会告诉你哪个按钮
-Is it this button? -I will tell you which button.

806
00:47:48,160 --> 00:47:49,240
-那这个按钮呢？-我很抱歉
-What about this button? -I'm sorry.

807
00:47:49,450 --> 00:47:51,200
我们没有时间去看所有的按钮了
We're not gonna have time to go over all the buttons.

808
00:47:51,370 --> 00:47:52,830
好吧 忘了这个按钮 那这个东西呢？
Okay, forget the button. What about this thing?

809
00:47:52,990 --> 00:47:53,830
-它更-- -不！不！ 不！
-It's more-- -No! No!

810
00:47:53,990 --> 00:47:56,120
那是投降线 你千万别拉那个
That's the surrender strand. You never pull that.

811
00:47:56,290 --> 00:47:58,620
对于太空游侠来说 没有比这更可耻的举动了
There is no more shameful maneuver for a Space Ranger.

812
00:47:58,790 --> 00:47:59,790
打扰一下
Excuse me.

813
00:47:59,960 --> 00:48:02,170
我是不是错过了哪个按钮是隐身模式的按钮？
Did I miss which button is the Stealth Mode button?

814
00:48:02,340 --> 00:48:03,420
是这个按钮
It's this button.

815
00:48:03,590 --> 00:48:04,630
还不行！
Not yet!

816
00:48:04,800 --> 00:48:07,550
你按下这个按钮 然后你就从前门出去
You push this button, then you go out the front door,

817
00:48:07,720 --> 00:48:09,510
然后我就去炸掉Zurg的船
and I'll go blow up the Zurg ship.

818
00:48:09,680 --> 00:48:11,090
-准备好了吗？-准备好了
-Ready? -Ready.

819
00:48:11,300 --> 00:48:13,100
不 等等 还没准备好 等一下
No, wait. Not ready. Hang on.

820
00:48:13,260 --> 00:48:15,180
好了 搞定他们了 这将一直是尴尬的
Okay, got 'em. That would've been embarrassing.

821
00:48:16,730 --> 00:48:17,730
好的
Okay.

822
00:48:17,890 --> 00:48:18,980
再见了
Goodbye again.

823
00:48:25,270 --> 00:48:27,280
索克斯 你抑制了我的视觉
Sox, you're inhibiting my visual.

824
00:48:27,440 --> 00:48:28,780
对不起 这样好些了吗？
Sorry. Is this better?

825
00:48:28,950 --> 00:48:30,780
-不对 -好吧 这个怎么样？
-Negative. -Okay, how about this?

826
00:48:31,530 --> 00:48:32,740
这样如何？
How about this?

827
00:48:44,750 --> 00:48:46,550
好的 我们开始吧
Okay. Here we go.

828
00:48:53,640 --> 00:48:56,180
非常好 隐形模式按计划进行
Very good. Stealth Mode working as planned.

829
00:48:57,620 --> 00:49:01,060
这真是太酷了 这些愚蠢的虫子甚至不能看到我们
This is pretty cool. These dumb bugs can't even see us.

830
00:49:01,320 --> 00:49:03,150
嘿 虫子 嘿 虫子 虫子
Hey, bug. Hey, bug. Bug.

831
00:49:03,360 --> 00:49:04,820
我就在这里 虫子 你看不到我吗？
I'm right here, bug. Can't you see me?

832
00:49:06,440 --> 00:49:08,940
他不能 他根本就看不到我
He can't. He can't see me at all.

833
00:49:09,240 --> 00:49:11,360
而且时间已经过了
And time has elapsed.

834
00:49:12,360 --> 00:49:13,660
等等 定时器
Wait, the timer.

835
00:49:13,870 --> 00:49:15,240
他们不知道定时器
They don't know about the timer.

836
00:49:16,870 --> 00:49:18,620
你没有看到我
You don't see me.

837
00:49:18,790 --> 00:49:20,040
等等 我可以看到你
Wait. I can see you.

838
00:49:20,790 --> 00:49:21,960
我也能看到你
I can see you too.

839
00:49:22,580 --> 00:49:23,920
虫子们能看到我们
The bugs can see us.

840
00:49:24,460 --> 00:49:26,090
不 不 我投降了
No, no. I surrender.

841
00:49:28,060 --> 00:49:29,200
拉！
Pull!

842
00:49:33,970 --> 00:49:35,510
后退！后退！
Back! Back!

843
00:49:37,680 --> 00:49:39,020
这不管用
This isn't working.

844
00:49:39,180 --> 00:49:40,560
你必须继续前进！
You have to keep going!

845
00:49:41,690 --> 00:49:43,600
我们必须掉头
We have to turn around.

846
00:49:45,650 --> 00:49:46,690
他们正朝我们走来
They're headed right for us.

847
00:49:46,860 --> 00:49:49,070
不 不 不要靠近那辆车！
No, no. Do not approach the vehicle!

848
00:50:03,210 --> 00:50:04,210
好的！
All right!

849
00:50:04,370 --> 00:50:05,830
-适应的方式 团队 -在这里交出它
-Way to adapt, team. -Give it up here.

850
00:50:06,000 --> 00:50:07,920
你们为什么要祝贺自己？
Why are you congratulating yourselves?

851
00:50:08,070 --> 00:50:10,200
因为我刚刚把我们从那种情况下山楂出来了
Because I just Hawthorned us out right outta that situation.

852
00:50:10,290 --> 00:50:11,730
但你本可以做到的 如果...
But you could've made it if--

853
00:50:11,830 --> 00:50:13,340
如果你告诉我们隐身模式会失效
If you had told us the Stealth Mode wears off.

854
00:50:13,430 --> 00:50:14,130
好吧...
Well...

855
00:50:16,090 --> 00:50:18,260
好了 大家系好安全带
Okay, everyone just strap in.

856
00:50:21,730 --> 00:50:22,770
你好 我是你的...
Hello, I am your--

857
00:50:35,410 --> 00:50:36,200
等一下！
Hold on!

858
00:50:40,910 --> 00:50:41,950
我们要去太空吗？
Are we going to space?

859
00:50:42,120 --> 00:50:43,580
不 我要把你放在某个地方
No, I'm gonna drop you somewhere.

860
00:50:47,250 --> 00:50:49,380
这是个大漩涡 我想我需要一个袋子
That was a big swirly turn. I think I need a bag.

861
00:50:49,550 --> 00:50:51,130
不 不 不要在车内呕吐
No, no. Do not vomit inside the vehicle.

862
00:50:51,300 --> 00:50:53,470
我可以看到开始 那是空间
I can see starts. That is space.

863
00:50:53,630 --> 00:50:54,720
现在是什么情况？
What is happening right now?

864
00:50:54,880 --> 00:50:55,930
她害怕空间
She's afraid of space.

865
00:50:56,090 --> 00:50:57,390
-什么？ -她应该是 太可怕了
-What? -She should be. It's horrible

866
00:50:57,550 --> 00:50:59,510
伊兹 记住你的练习
Izzy, remember your exercises.

867
00:50:59,680 --> 00:51:00,930
-它要来了 -不 不
-It's coming. -No, no.

868
00:51:01,100 --> 00:51:02,060
把你的头盔接合起来 那会抓住它的
Engage your helmet. That will catch it.

869
00:51:02,220 --> 00:51:03,770
-嗡嗡声！另一艘飞船！-伊兹 我正在努力... ...
-Buzz! Another ship! -Izzy, I'm trying--

870
00:51:26,670 --> 00:51:27,670
我什么都看不见了
I can't see anything.

871
00:51:27,830 --> 00:51:29,590
哦 不！地球的黑暗面
Oh, no! The dark side of the planet.

872
00:51:29,750 --> 00:51:30,960
在那里！三点钟方向！
Over there! Three o'clock!

873
00:51:31,130 --> 00:51:33,380
坚持住 这不会是件好事
Hold on. This isn't gonna be pretty.

874
00:51:44,140 --> 00:51:45,140
大家都还好吗？
Is everyone okay?

875
00:51:45,310 --> 00:51:46,140
我想是的
I think so.

876
00:51:56,450 --> 00:51:57,610
索克斯 给我一份损害报告
Sox, give me a damage report.

877
00:51:57,780 --> 00:51:59,450
请稍等
One moment, please.

878
00:52:01,200 --> 00:52:03,040
好的 这样就好了
Okay. This is better.

879
00:52:03,490 --> 00:52:04,620
这是更好吗？
Is this better?

880
00:52:04,790 --> 00:52:08,500
不 显然这是更糟糕的整体 我只是意味着... 你知道...
No, obviously this is worse overall, I just meant... You know...

881
00:52:09,330 --> 00:52:10,750
你怎么会害怕太空？
How are you afraid of space?

882
00:52:11,250 --> 00:52:12,340
哦 这很容易
Oh, It's pretty easy.

883
00:52:12,670 --> 00:52:16,170
你知道吗 如果你在外面放任自流 你就会一直朝着同一个方向前进
Did you know if you let go out there you just keep going in the same direction

884
00:52:16,340 --> 00:52:18,340
永远 只是...
forever, just...

885
00:52:18,630 --> 00:52:21,140
好吧 那你打算怎么炸掉Zurg的船？
Well, then how were you going to blow up the Zurg ship?

886
00:52:21,300 --> 00:52:23,100
我本来是做地面支援的
I would've been ground support.

887
00:52:24,140 --> 00:52:26,180
我知道 奶奶并不害怕太空
I know, grandma wasn't afraid of space.

888
00:52:26,350 --> 00:52:28,270
不 因为她是一名太空游侠
No, because she was a Space Ranger.

889
00:52:28,440 --> 00:52:30,940
天体恐惧症是自动取消资格的
Astrophobia is an automatic disqualification.

890
00:52:31,100 --> 00:52:32,400
那是什么东西？
What was that thing?

891
00:52:32,610 --> 00:52:34,110
-我不知道 -它还会回来吗？
-I don't know. -Is it gonna come back?

892
00:52:34,270 --> 00:52:35,400
我不知道
I don't know.

893
00:52:35,570 --> 00:52:37,900
但它是怎么... ... 好吧 你不知道
But how did it-- Okay, you don't know.

894
00:52:42,030 --> 00:52:45,370
我已经完成了 我终于拿到了水晶 这本来应该结束的
I was done. I finally had the crystal. This was supposed to be over.

895
00:52:46,200 --> 00:52:47,580
但我在骗谁呢？
But who am I kidding?

896
00:52:48,540 --> 00:52:49,920
我不需要水晶
I don't need a crystal.

897
00:52:50,000 --> 00:52:52,040
我需要一台时间机器来摆脱这种混乱
I need a time machine to get out of this mess.

898
00:52:52,750 --> 00:52:54,000
评估完成
Assessment complete.

899
00:52:54,170 --> 00:52:55,170
这有多糟？
How bad is that?

900
00:52:57,260 --> 00:53:01,300
爆炸被挡热板吸收了 只造成了轻微的电气短路
The blast was absorbed by the heat shield and only caused a minor electrical short.

901
00:53:01,470 --> 00:53:02,470
好的
Okay.

902
00:53:02,640 --> 00:53:04,100
那么 为了能在飞行中使用
So, in order to be flight operational

903
00:53:04,260 --> 00:53:07,640
犰狳需要一种特殊电容的材料
the Armadillo will require a material of specialized capacitance.

904
00:53:07,850 --> 00:53:09,100
哦 就像一个电气的东西
Oh, like an electrical thingy.

905
00:53:09,270 --> 00:53:10,270
你怎么知道的？
How do you know that?

906
00:53:10,440 --> 00:53:11,480
我们学过这个
We learned this.

907
00:53:12,560 --> 00:53:15,900
专门的电容 记得吗？我们上个月做了那些野外收音机？
Specialized capacitance, remember? We built those field radios last month?

908
00:53:16,070 --> 00:53:17,110
哦 是的 那很有趣
Oh, yeah. That was fun.

909
00:53:17,280 --> 00:53:18,400
是的 除了达比把她的弄乱了
Yeah, except Darby messed hers up.

910
00:53:18,570 --> 00:53:19,570
我要把你弄得一团糟 --
I'm gonna mess you up--

911
00:53:19,740 --> 00:53:21,570
拜讬了 我正在努力思考
Please. I'm trying to think here.

912
00:53:22,030 --> 00:53:23,870
我把我的弄乱了 但我又把它修好了
I messed mine up, but then I fixed it up.

913
00:53:24,030 --> 00:53:25,370
但是你弄坏了那个电脑控制台
But you broke that computer console.

914
00:53:25,530 --> 00:53:27,620
我需要那个小线圈来... 那是什么？
I needed that little coil for its... What was that?

915
00:53:27,790 --> 00:53:28,830
专门的电容
Specialized capacitance.

916
00:53:29,000 --> 00:53:31,290
嘿 说实话 这里有很多空间
Hey, honestly, there is a lot of room out here.

917
00:53:31,460 --> 00:53:34,210
如果你们想回忆一下 你们可以到那边去
If you guys wanna reminisce you could go over there,

918
00:53:34,380 --> 00:53:36,550
或者看 那里没有人想去思考
or look, there's no one trying to think over there.

919
00:53:37,590 --> 00:53:38,630
我们可以到上面去
We can go up there.

920
00:53:38,800 --> 00:53:39,800
好吧 完美
Fine. Perfect.

921
00:53:39,970 --> 00:53:42,220
是的 好的 新计划
Yes. Okay, new plan.

922
00:53:42,380 --> 00:53:43,390
等等 什么？
Wait. What?

923
00:53:43,550 --> 00:53:45,600
那个采矿设施会有一个控制台 对吗？
That mining facility will have a console, right?

924
00:53:45,760 --> 00:53:48,140
那个控制台会有一个小线圈 对吗？
That console will have a little coil thing, right?

925
00:53:48,310 --> 00:53:49,980
而那个小线圈的东西会有...
And that little coil thing will have the...

926
00:53:50,140 --> 00:53:51,140
专门的电容
Specialized capacitance.

927
00:53:51,310 --> 00:53:53,650
我们需要修复这艘船 对吗？
That we need to fix this ship, right?

928
00:53:53,810 --> 00:53:54,650
她是对的
She's right.

929
00:53:57,940 --> 00:54:01,110
做得好 这就是霍桑人的思维方式
Good job. Now that's thinking like a Hawthorne.

930
00:54:02,300 --> 00:54:04,940
我们去拿那个零件 然后离开这里吧
Let's go get that part and get outta here

931
00:54:05,040 --> 00:54:06,990
在那东西再次找到我们之前
before that thing finds us again.

932
00:54:29,060 --> 00:54:30,310
哇
Whoa.

933
00:54:31,270 --> 00:54:32,430
在那边
Over there.

934
00:54:35,730 --> 00:54:37,270
好了 我们走吧
Okay, here we go.

935
00:54:45,700 --> 00:54:47,200
巴斯光年任务日志
Buzz Lightyear mission log.

936
00:54:47,370 --> 00:54:49,990
为了修复我们的飞船 我们必须找到一些方法
In order to repair our ship we have to find some way

937
00:54:50,160 --> 00:54:52,040
进入指挥中心并...
to get inside the Command Center and...

938
00:54:54,210 --> 00:54:56,250
干得好 老犯人
Nice job, elderly convict.

939
00:54:58,090 --> 00:55:01,380
好的 激活线圈应该在这里
Okay, the activation coil should be in here.

940
00:55:01,550 --> 00:55:02,550
索克斯？
Sox?

941
00:55:03,840 --> 00:55:04,840
需要一支笔吗？
Need a pen?

942
00:55:04,930 --> 00:55:06,640
知道了
Got it.

943
00:55:07,510 --> 00:55:08,800
好的 是的 再来一次
Okay, yeah. Another time.

944
00:55:10,470 --> 00:55:11,470
哦 不
Oh no.

945
00:55:11,810 --> 00:55:13,600
安全措施启动
Security measures activated.

946
00:55:14,690 --> 00:55:16,650
不 不能再这样了
No! Not this again.

947
00:55:16,810 --> 00:55:18,020
不是什么？这是什么？
Not what? What is this?

948
00:55:18,360 --> 00:55:23,070
一个捕获锥 在他们来抓你之前 它能把你关起来
A capture cone. That holds you until they come and get you.

949
00:55:23,240 --> 00:55:25,360
没有人会来救我们 他们都被困在基地里了
No one's coming to get us. They're all trapped in the base.

950
00:55:25,530 --> 00:55:26,700
所以 我们应该离开 对吗？
So, we should just leave, right?

951
00:55:26,860 --> 00:55:28,280
我们不能就这样离开
We can't just leave.

952
00:55:28,450 --> 00:55:31,410
当然 我们可以 听我说 我们总是可以离开的
Sure we can. Take it from me, we can always just leave.

953
00:55:32,080 --> 00:55:33,080
看 看到了吗？
Look, see?

954
00:55:34,540 --> 00:55:35,620
来吧！
Come on!

955
00:55:36,920 --> 00:55:37,920
我告诉过你
Told you.

956
00:55:38,420 --> 00:55:41,250
现在 要小心 因为这些东西 --
Now, be careful, because these things--

957
00:55:42,210 --> 00:55:44,010
如果它们碰在一起 就会结合起来
combine if they touch.

958
00:55:44,170 --> 00:55:46,720
好吧 对不起 但也许如果我们两个都试一下？
All right, sorry. But maybe if we both try it?

959
00:55:46,880 --> 00:55:48,590
那是不可能的
That's not gonna work.

960
00:55:48,760 --> 00:55:50,010
你甚至都没试过
You haven't even tried.

961
00:55:51,390 --> 00:55:52,390
不！
No!

962
00:55:52,740 --> 00:55:53,570
喵喵
Meow.

963
00:55:55,020 --> 00:55:56,140
是的 那没有用
Yeah, that didn't work.

964
00:55:56,300 --> 00:55:57,640
-巴兹？-哇 坚持住
-Buzz? -Whoa, hold on.

965
00:55:57,810 --> 00:55:59,940
如果我和你一起被困在那里 我对任何人都没有帮助
I'm no help to anyone if I'm stuck in there with you.

966
00:56:00,110 --> 00:56:01,570
索克斯 你能把这些关掉吗？
Sox, can you turn these off?

967
00:56:02,860 --> 00:56:04,610
我够不到控制装置
I can't reach the controls.

968
00:56:05,320 --> 00:56:07,490
等等 这里的地板上有个软点
Wait, there's a soft spot in the floor here.

969
00:56:07,650 --> 00:56:09,030
-也许我们可以... ... -那是我的脚
-Maybe if we could-- -That's my foot.

970
00:56:09,620 --> 00:56:10,820
-对不起 -等等 小心！
-Sorry. -Wait, watch it!

971
00:56:11,830 --> 00:56:14,700
等等 就是这个 那东西给这些东西提供了动力
Wait, that's it. That thing powers these things.

972
00:56:14,870 --> 00:56:16,960
-那我们就再打一次 -等等 等一下
-Then let's hit it again. -Wait. Wait.

973
00:56:17,620 --> 00:56:19,120
我们需要门是开着的
We need the door to be open.

974
00:56:19,290 --> 00:56:22,290
那么我就打开这个 你猛地撞上电源
So I'll open this. You slam into the power source.

975
00:56:22,460 --> 00:56:24,880
这些东西会消失 然后我们就可以走出去了
These things will disappear. And we'll walk right out.

976
00:56:25,050 --> 00:56:25,880
-是的 先生 -好的
-Yes, sir. -All right.

977
00:56:26,050 --> 00:56:26,840
准备好了吗？
Ready?

978
00:56:31,090 --> 00:56:31,800
继续努力！
Keep trying!

979
00:56:36,350 --> 00:56:37,810
我们只是不够重
We're just not heavy enough.

980
00:56:38,520 --> 00:56:40,270
巴斯 我们需要你
Buzz, we need you.

981
00:56:40,440 --> 00:56:41,730
等等 在那里？
Wait, in there?

982
00:56:41,900 --> 00:56:44,150
但如果不成功 我就不能救你们了
But if it doesn't work I won't be able to save you.

983
00:56:44,320 --> 00:56:47,190
你不需要救我们 你需要加入我们
You don't need to save us, you need to join us.

984
00:56:55,410 --> 00:56:56,410
再来
Again.

985
00:56:57,960 --> 00:57:02,460
再来！
Again!

986
00:57:09,380 --> 00:57:10,470
不！
No!

987
00:57:11,260 --> 00:57:12,300
走！快走！
Go! Go!

988
00:57:13,760 --> 00:57:14,760
小心点！
Watch out!

989
00:57:19,060 --> 00:57:20,060
巴斯 不要！
Buzz, no!

990
00:57:20,230 --> 00:57:21,400
我们需要线圈
We need the coil.

991
00:57:39,410 --> 00:57:40,790
我们得到了你
We got you.

992
00:57:49,840 --> 00:57:50,970
哦 看 零食
Oh, look. Snacks.

993
00:57:53,180 --> 00:57:54,470
有人要吃零食吗？
Anyone going for the snack?

994
00:57:55,350 --> 00:57:57,850
肉类三明治
MEAT SANDWICH

995
00:58:04,150 --> 00:58:06,610
这里 让我们都再充点电吧
Here. Let's all re-charge a little.

996
00:58:09,820 --> 00:58:10,940
给你
Here you go.

997
00:58:13,470 --> 00:58:17,160
嗯 这是 呃--什么--什么--
Huh, this is, uh-- What-- What's--

998
00:58:17,830 --> 00:58:18,990
这里发生了什么？
What's happening here?

999
00:58:19,410 --> 00:58:20,620
你的三文治有问题吗？
Something wrong with your sandwich?

1000
00:58:20,790 --> 00:58:23,370
为什么肉在外面？
Why is the meat on the outside?

1001
00:58:23,710 --> 00:58:25,330
因为它是一个三明治？
Because it's a sandwich?

1002
00:58:25,500 --> 00:58:27,500
不 面包应该是在外面的
No, the bread is supposed to be on the outside.

1003
00:58:27,670 --> 00:58:29,210
什么 比如 面包 肉 面包？
What, like, bread, meat, bread?

1004
00:58:29,380 --> 00:58:30,550
那是太多的面包了
That's too much bread.

1005
00:58:31,050 --> 00:58:32,800
是的 但这都是湿的
Yes, but this is all wet.

1006
00:58:32,970 --> 00:58:35,010
是的 多汁的手指 那是最好的部分
Yeah. Juicy fingers. That's the best part.

1007
00:58:35,180 --> 00:58:36,850
你上次吃三明治是什么时候？
When was the last time you had a sandwich?

1008
00:58:37,010 --> 00:58:39,050
我不知道 一百年前 差不多吧
I don't know, a hundred years ago, give or take.

1009
00:58:39,220 --> 00:58:41,180
只是一个 "面包 肉 面包"
Just a "bread, meat, bread."

1010
00:58:41,350 --> 00:58:42,350
那是太多的面包了
That's too much bread.

1011
00:58:42,520 --> 00:58:44,600
那会把你嘴里的水分都吸走的
That would just suck all the moisture out of your mouth.

1012
00:58:45,560 --> 00:58:46,560
说得好 达比
Good one, Darby.

1013
00:58:46,900 --> 00:58:47,940
哦 不！
Oh, no!

1014
00:58:48,150 --> 00:58:49,020
索克斯！
Sox!

1015
00:58:50,230 --> 00:58:51,440
醒醒吧 索克斯
Wake up, Sox.

1016
00:58:51,990 --> 00:58:53,570
来吧 小家伙 回到我身边
Come on, little buddy, come back to me.

1017
00:58:54,200 --> 00:58:55,660
求你了 索克斯 我很抱歉
Please, Sox. I'm sorry.

1018
00:58:56,490 --> 00:58:57,490
索克斯
Sox.

1019
00:58:59,910 --> 00:59:01,620
你好 我需要重启
Hello. I require a reboot.

1020
00:59:06,790 --> 00:59:10,670
我很抱歉 夥计们 我差点杀了索克斯
I'm sorry, guys. I almost killed Sox.

1021
00:59:10,960 --> 00:59:13,090
我差点把我们都害死了 在那里
I almost got us all killed back there.

1022
00:59:13,260 --> 00:59:16,510
嘿 听我说 这只是一个错误
Hey, listen to me, it was just a mistake.

1023
00:59:17,140 --> 00:59:18,140
对吧 巴兹？
Right, Buzz?

1024
00:59:20,510 --> 00:59:24,140
试着让自己变得更好一点
Just try to get a little better.

1025
00:59:30,620 --> 00:59:31,660
听着
Listen.

1026
00:59:34,490 --> 00:59:36,070
我只是...
I just...

1027
00:59:37,030 --> 00:59:42,620
当我第一次去学院的时候 我并不... 你知道... 好
When I first went to the Academy I was not... you know... good.

1028
00:59:43,620 --> 00:59:46,170
我每天都搞砸了
I screwed up every day.

1029
00:59:47,750 --> 00:59:49,130
我在障碍赛中被缠住了
I got tangled in the obstacle course.

1030
00:59:49,290 --> 00:59:51,920
我的手抖得厉害 无法打中目标
My hands shook so much I couldn't hit the target.

1031
00:59:52,090 --> 00:59:54,760
不是指牛眼 是整个目标
Not the bulls-eye. The whole target.

1032
00:59:55,510 --> 00:59:57,800
第一周后 我打算退出 因为... ...
And I was gonna quit after the first week, it was...

1033
00:59:57,970 --> 01:00:00,890
显然我不是太空游侠的料
clear I was not Space Ranger material.

1034
01:00:01,050 --> 01:00:02,100
真的吗？
Really?

1035
01:00:02,510 --> 01:00:03,560
是的
Yeah.

1036
01:00:04,020 --> 01:00:06,100
但她的祖母在我身上看到了一些东西
But her grandma saw something in me.

1037
01:00:08,650 --> 01:00:10,190
所以我也开始寻找它
So I started looking for it too.

1038
01:00:12,360 --> 01:00:13,360
重新校准
Recalibrating.

1039
01:00:14,780 --> 01:00:17,110
一个损坏的文件恢复了
One corrupted file restored.

1040
01:00:18,910 --> 01:00:20,120
嘿 他亮了
Hey, he's lighting up.

1041
01:00:20,990 --> 01:00:23,160
-奶奶 -你好 索克斯
-Grandma. -Hello, Sox.

1042
01:00:23,330 --> 01:00:25,040
我需要你帮我一个忙
I need you to do me a favor.

1043
01:00:25,200 --> 01:00:29,210
我需要你照顾我最好的朋友 他的名字叫巴兹
I need you to look after my best friend. His name is Buzz.

1044
01:00:29,790 --> 01:00:33,340
他现在不在 但他很快就会回来
He's away right now, but he'll be back soon.

1045
01:00:33,500 --> 01:00:35,510
他是一名太空游侠
He's a Space Ranger.

1046
01:00:35,670 --> 01:00:38,550
他要把我们都带回家 让我们都回家
He's going to get us all home. Get us all home.

1047
01:00:53,110 --> 01:00:54,360
怎么了？
What's wrong?

1048
01:00:54,900 --> 01:00:56,190
你没听到吗？
Did not you hear that?

1049
01:00:56,570 --> 01:00:58,950
她相信我可以弥补我犯的错误
She believed I could fix the mistake I made.

1050
01:00:59,780 --> 01:01:01,950
而这种信念让她失去了一切
And that belief cost her everything.

1051
01:01:02,820 --> 01:01:04,700
一切？不是
Everything? No.

1052
01:01:05,490 --> 01:01:08,830
她有基科奶奶 我爸爸和我 她所有的朋友
She had grandma Kiko, my Dad and me, all her friends.

1053
01:01:09,790 --> 01:01:13,880
她本不应该在这里 但她在这个星球上有一个完整的生命 巴兹
She didn't meant to be here, but she had a whole life on this planet, Buzz.

1054
01:01:14,710 --> 01:01:15,880
我们所有人都有
All of us had.

1055
01:01:17,050 --> 01:01:18,760
除了你
Except for you.

1056
01:01:21,130 --> 01:01:25,390
我们想再次成为太空骑兵 我们想成为重要人物
We wanted to be Space Rangers again. We wanted to matter.

1057
01:01:26,600 --> 01:01:29,430
相信我 她很重要
Believe me, she mattered.

1058
01:01:42,240 --> 01:01:43,820
你知道 这样很好
You know, it is pretty good this way.

1059
01:01:44,410 --> 01:01:48,370
是吗？面包 肉 面包 你这样做了多长时间？
Yeah? Bread, meat, bread. How long did you do it like that?

1060
01:01:48,910 --> 01:01:49,910
永远
Forever.

1061
01:01:52,170 --> 01:01:53,540
完全充电
Fully recharged.

1062
01:01:53,790 --> 01:01:54,960
来吧
Come on.

1063
01:01:55,130 --> 01:01:57,710
我们去把这部分放到船上 然后离开这里
Let's go put this part in the ship and get outta here.

1064
01:01:58,300 --> 01:01:59,300
索克斯 你能照亮我们的路吗？
Sox, can you light our way?

1065
01:01:59,460 --> 01:02:00,470
当然可以
Of course.

1066
01:02:00,570 --> 01:02:03,310
卡嚓 卡嚓
Click click. Click click.

1067
01:02:03,930 --> 01:02:06,640
我看到你了 我要抓住你 我要抓住你
I see you. I'm gonna get ya. I'm gonna get ya.

1068
01:02:06,800 --> 01:02:07,590
哦 我没有得到你
Oh, I didn't get ya.

1069
01:02:07,760 --> 01:02:09,430
