是的
Yeah.

1154
01:08:37,030 --> 01:08:39,410
好吧 但我们还没有完成 对吗？
Okay, but we're not done, right?

1155
01:08:39,990 --> 01:08:41,620
我们仍然可以做一些事情
We can still do something.

1156
01:08:41,780 --> 01:08:44,040
伊兹 看看周围
Izzy, look around.

1157
01:08:44,620 --> 01:08:46,210
没有什么可做的
There is nothing to do.

1158
01:08:46,370 --> 01:08:47,460
这个任务...
The mission...

1159
01:08:48,750 --> 01:08:49,920
已经结束了
It's over.

1160
01:08:50,670 --> 01:08:51,790
巴斯
Buzz.

1161
01:08:52,250 --> 01:08:53,420
巴斯！
Buzz!

1162
01:08:53,590 --> 01:08:55,050
你要去哪里？
Where are you going?

1163
01:08:55,210 --> 01:08:58,380
我只是需要一个人静一静
I just need to be by myself.

1164
01:09:01,300 --> 01:09:02,300
不！
No!

1165
01:09:08,560 --> 01:09:09,560
巴斯！
Buzz!

1166
01:09:12,560 --> 01:09:13,560
巴斯！
Buzz.

1167
01:09:46,640 --> 01:09:47,640
这是什么...
What the...

1168
01:09:47,970 --> 01:09:50,430
这是什么？我们在哪里？
What is this? Where are we?

1169
01:09:51,480 --> 01:09:52,600
你是谁？
Who are you?

1170
01:09:52,900 --> 01:09:54,690
这就是问题所在
Now that's the question.

1171
01:10:05,240 --> 01:10:07,080
你看起来不错 巴兹
You look good, Buzz.

1172
01:10:08,200 --> 01:10:09,330
爸爸？
Dad?

1173
01:10:09,580 --> 01:10:10,580
再猜猜看
Guess again.

1174
01:10:25,470 --> 01:10:26,470
索克斯？
Sox?

1175
01:10:27,810 --> 01:10:29,310
你好 巴兹
Hello, Buzz.

1176
01:10:30,180 --> 01:10:31,640
我不明白
I don't understand.

1177
01:10:37,860 --> 01:10:39,150
我把这一切都搞砸了
I messed this all up.

1178
01:10:39,320 --> 01:10:41,280
嘿 这只是一个错误
Hey, it was just a mistake.

1179
01:10:41,780 --> 01:10:43,110
还记得你告诉我的吗？
Remember what you told me?

1180
01:10:43,990 --> 01:10:45,070
这一次是不同的
This one's different.

1181
01:10:45,240 --> 01:10:46,240
为什么？
Why?

1182
01:10:46,410 --> 01:10:47,830
因为这是我的！
Because it's mine!

1183
01:10:59,670 --> 01:11:02,590
我应该和我奶奶一样好
I'm supposed to be as good as my grandma.

1184
01:11:03,180 --> 01:11:05,260
我应该是霍桑的人
I'm supposed to be a Hawthorne.

1185
01:11:08,180 --> 01:11:09,350
但我不是
But I'm not.

1186
01:11:22,690 --> 01:11:23,820
巴兹？
Buzz?

1187
01:11:25,990 --> 01:11:27,160
等一下 等一下
Wait a minute, hold on.

1188
01:11:27,320 --> 01:11:28,620
你不是我 我是我
You're not me. I am me.

1189
01:11:28,780 --> 01:11:29,830
你现在是你
You are you now.

1190
01:11:29,990 --> 01:11:32,000
但我是50年后的你
But I'm you 50 years from now.

1191
01:11:32,160 --> 01:11:33,330
好吧 不可能有两个MES
Well, there can't be two mes.

1192
01:11:33,500 --> 01:11:35,000
但我们都在这里
Yet here we both are.

1193
01:11:35,670 --> 01:11:37,040
那么好吧 如果你是我
Okay then. If you're me.

1194
01:11:37,210 --> 01:11:38,880
我在想一个介于1和 --
I'm thinking of a number between one and--

1195
01:11:39,040 --> 01:11:40,630
1273.
1273.

1196
01:11:40,800 --> 01:11:41,800
哇哦
Whoa.

1197
01:11:42,770 --> 01:11:43,670
祖格
Zurg.

1198
01:11:43,760 --> 01:11:45,090
这不是很可爱吗？
Isn't that cute.

1199
01:11:45,260 --> 01:11:46,970
机器人不能完全说 "嗡嗡"
Robots can't quite say "Buzz."

1200
01:11:47,180 --> 01:11:49,420
所以在这里我就叫祖格
So around here I'm just Zurg.

1201
01:11:49,510 --> 01:11:50,350
扎克
Zurg.

1202
01:11:50,430 --> 01:11:51,520
我想你也是
And I guess so are you.

1203
01:11:51,680 --> 01:11:52,680
怎么会呢？我不明白
How? I don't understand.

1204
01:11:52,850 --> 01:11:54,810
不要担心 这一切都不重要了
Do not worry about it. None of this is gonna matter.

1205
01:11:54,980 --> 01:11:55,810
巴兹
Buzz.

1206
01:11:55,980 --> 01:11:56,850
什么事？
Yes?

1207
01:11:57,020 --> 01:11:58,560
你必须向他解释这一切
You have to explain it all to him.

1208
01:11:59,360 --> 01:12:00,360
你是对的
You're right.

1209
01:12:00,520 --> 01:12:02,820
我很抱歉 这只是令人兴奋
I'm sorry, it's just exciting.

1210
01:12:02,990 --> 01:12:04,440
你终于来了
You're finally here.

1211
01:12:04,610 --> 01:12:07,070
看 我也达到了超速
See, I reached hyper-speed too.

1212
01:12:07,490 --> 01:12:08,950
超速
Hyper-speed.

1213
01:12:09,660 --> 01:12:11,200
和你一样
Like you did.

1214
01:12:12,080 --> 01:12:14,450
但我没有被当作英雄来迎接
But I wasn't greeted as a hero.

1215
01:12:15,410 --> 01:12:20,380
不 那个新指挥官要以偷窃XL-15的罪名逮捕我
No, that new Commander was gonna  arrest me for stealing the XL-15.

1216
01:12:20,540 --> 01:12:24,170
我找到了一个让他们回家的方法 而他们甚至都不在乎
I'd found a way to get them home, and they didn't even care.

1217
01:12:24,340 --> 01:12:25,300
所以我逃了出来
So I escaped.

1218
01:12:30,760 --> 01:12:34,020
我尽可能地走得远 尽可能地快
I went as far as I could, as fast as I could.

1219
01:12:34,680 --> 01:12:37,940
以这种速度走了那么久 我已经走了几个世纪
At that speed for that long I'd traveled centuries.

1220
01:12:38,100 --> 01:12:41,900
而我最终来到了一个你不认识的未来
And I ended up in a future you wouldn』t recognize.

1221
01:12:42,110 --> 01:12:44,690
充满了你无法想像的技术
Filled with technology you can't imagine.

1222
01:12:45,070 --> 01:12:47,530
就在那时 我恍然大悟
And that's when it dawned on me.

1223
01:12:47,700 --> 01:12:50,950
如果我们能用这块水晶向前推进时间
If we can use this crystal  to go forward in time.

1224
01:12:51,830 --> 01:12:53,370
为什么不能用它来回到过去呢？
Why not use it to go back?

1225
01:12:53,540 --> 01:12:55,200
但我们不能回到过去
But we can't go back in time.

1226
01:12:55,370 --> 01:12:57,160
-我们现在可以 -什么？
-We can now. -What?

1227
01:12:57,370 --> 01:13:00,330
听着 巴兹 我已经打破了时间
Listen, Buzz, I've broken time.

1228
01:13:00,500 --> 01:13:03,510
发生在你身上的事从未发生在我身上
What's happening to you never happened to me.

1229
01:13:03,710 --> 01:13:07,050
这是个全新的现在 从来没有过的
This is a new now that's never been lived.

1230
01:13:07,220 --> 01:13:09,680
你看 我们可以改变事情 巴兹
You see, we can change things, Buzz.

1231
01:13:09,840 --> 01:13:13,890
如果我们能回到过去 我们可以阻止自己
Well, if we can go back in time  we can stop ourselves

1232
01:13:14,060 --> 01:13:15,020
我们可以阻止自己降落在那个星球上
from ever landing on that planet.

1233
01:13:15,180 --> 01:13:16,350
不去撞上那座山
From ever hitting that mountain.

1234
01:13:16,520 --> 01:13:17,850
我们可以继续完成回家的任务
We can just continue the mission home.

1235
01:13:18,020 --> 01:13:19,650
而这一切都不会发生
And none of this will have ever happened.

1236
01:13:20,310 --> 01:13:21,730
这是个好计划
it's a good plan.

1237
01:13:22,020 --> 01:13:24,400
而这个水晶是这一切的关键
And this crystal is the key to it all.

1238
01:13:24,570 --> 01:13:26,030
等等 你不是已经有一个了吗？
Wait, don't you already have one?

1239
01:13:26,190 --> 01:13:27,690
嗯 算是吧
Well, sort of.

1240
01:13:28,990 --> 01:13:32,410
