Yeah.

1253
01:14:08,400 --> 01:14:09,400
虽然...
Although...

1254
01:14:09,570 --> 01:14:10,400
什么？
What?

1255
01:14:10,610 --> 01:14:13,530
嗯 她将不会有她的家人
Well, she won't have her family.

1256
01:14:14,120 --> 01:14:15,160
